              "base64": false,
              "type": "text/html",
              "value": "<p>The following software releases have been updated to resolve this specific issue: Junos OS 21.2R3-S5, 21.3R3-S5, 21.4R3-S4, 22.1R3-S3, 22.2R3-S1, 22.3R2-S2, 22.3R3, 22.4R2-S1, 22.4R3, 23.2R1, and all subsequent releases.</p>"
            }
          ],
          "value": "The following software releases have been updated to resolve this specific issue: Junos OS 21.2R3-S5, 21.3R3-S5, 21.4R3-S4, 22.1R3-S3, 22.2R3-S1, 22.3R2-S2, 22.3R3, 22.4R2-S1, 22.4R3, 23.2R1, and all subsequent releases.\n\n"
